snippet.title: Papu Superstars Racing - First Demo Trailer
snippet.description: Papu Superstars is a Free to Play Game Franchise where you can play with the characters of the NFT Collections you own, and compete representing your favourite community. A fun, polished and accessible gaming experience for any kind of player.
